A. B. Lonergan and F. L. Kendrick, Appellants, v. J. O. Peebles and Alice L. Peebles, his wife, The Banking Savings & Trust Company, a Corporation and J. H. Smithwick, Appellees. An Appeal from a Decree of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Santa Rosa. Nelson & Laird, for Appellants; Watson & Pasco, for Appellees.

Appeal dismissed on praecipe of counsel for appellants.
